snippet.title: Death Run 3D Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Store (Android): http://2ed.it/BAEv
Kongregate (PC): http://2ed.it/BAEw
Music by enV: http://2ed.it/BAEx

-Death Run 3D is an extremely addictive hardcore game! 
-If  you like hard challenges this is the game for you!
-Your goal is to survive as long as you can, are you up to the task?!
-The longer you survive, the harder it gets!
-Beat your own score, collect all the achievements and reach the top of the leaderboard!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/GamesKapo
